er. <P>Raging Power <BR>Big boost to power, usable in combat. <P>Purge <BR>Dispel all negative spell effects. <P>Corporeal Disintegration <BR>Area-effect DOT, stacks with other DOT lines.<P>--------------------<P>Frazier - 44 Briton Sorc
